    "rowNumber": 22,
    "key": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.173.Hee",
    "utterer": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.173.Hee",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "We have decided your Soul will not undergo Reassignment."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "8_asses.masses_E8Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E8_TheGods_localization",
    "entryIndex": 20,
    "rowNumber": 23,
    "key": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.186.Hee",
    "utterer": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.186.Hee",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "Instead, you have been selected for a Special Position and the highest privilege that we can bestow upon a Vassal."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "8_asses.masses_E8Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E8_TheGods_localization",
    "entryIndex": 21,
    "rowNumber": 24,
    "key": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.175.Haw",
    "utterer": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.175.Haw",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "As our godly burden is to carry the Universe upon our back, we cannot interfere in the Material World without putting all life at risk."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "8_asses.masses_E8Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E8_TheGods_localization",
    "entryIndex": 22,
    "rowNumber": 25,
    "key": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.193.Haw",
    "utterer": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.193.Haw",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "Thus, when we can, we elect a Vassal to be our Avatar."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "8_asses.masses_E8Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E8_TheGods_localization",
    "entryIndex": 23,
    "rowNumber": 26,
    "key": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.194.Haw",
    "utterer": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.194.Haw",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "It is through this Vassal, this \"Golden Ass\", that we return to the Material World and initiate our holy Revolutions."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "8_asses.masses_E8Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E8_TheGods_localization",
    "entryIndex": 24,
    "rowNumber": 27,
    "key": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.196.Hee",
    "utterer": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.196.Hee",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "Once upon a time, our Vassals and their labours were seen as sacred."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "8_asses.masses_E8Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E8_TheGods_localization",
    "entryIndex": 25,
    "rowNumber": 28,
    "key": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.197.Hee",
    "utterer": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.197.Hee",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "They were worshipped and loved by all for their generosity, especially by Humans."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "8_asses.masses_E8Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E8_TheGods_localization",
    "entryIndex": 26,
    "rowNumber": 29,
    "key": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.198.Hee",
    "utterer": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.198.Hee",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "But, after centuries of collaboration between Asses and Humans, our Vassals are worshipped no more."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "8_asses.masses_E8Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E8_TheGods_localization",
    "entryIndex": 27,
    "rowNumber": 30,
    "key": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.200.Hee",
    "utterer": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.200.Hee",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "The Humans, who once begged us for our Powers of Change and for whom we have fought so many wars, now play at being gods of change themselves."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "8_asses.masses_E8Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E8_TheGods_localization",
    "entryIndex": 28,
    "rowNumber": 31,
    "key": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.201.Hee",
    "utterer": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.201.Hee",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "Our Vassals now return to the Astral Plane shaken by endless suffering and corrupted by apathy."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "8_asses.masses_E8Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E8_TheGods_localization",
    "entryIndex": 29,
    "rowNumber": 32,
    "key": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.203.Haw",
    "utterer": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.203.Haw",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "The Humans' games must come to an end."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "8_asses.masses_E8Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E8_TheGods_localization",
    "entryIndex": 30,
    "rowNumber": 33,
    "key": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.204.Haw",
    "utterer": "SAY.Dialog:GODS.204.Haw",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "We look forward to working with you and rectifying this sorrowful situation."
  },
